            "weighting": "<dd>30% (3 Quizzes - 10% Each) </dd>",
            "due_date": "<dd><p>In-Tutorial Week 5,</p>\n<p>In-Tutorial Week 7,</p>\n<p>In-Tutorial Week 11,</p>\n<p>\n</p><p>Students will only be able to complete the quiz in their enrolled tutorial.</p></dd>",
            "learning_objectives": "L01, L02",
            "mode": "Written",
            "category": "Quiz",
            "task_description": "<div class=\"collapsible collapsible--text\">\n<p>Student IDs are mandatory. <strong>Students must present a valid university-issued ID card</strong> to be admitted into the room for the quiz. Without it, entry will not be permitted.</p>\n<p>Students are required to complete three in-class quizzes covering the materials</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Students will have 30 minutes to complete each quiz.</li>\n<li>There will be true/false, multiple choice, and numerical questions in this quiz. </li>\n<li>Students should be at the venue for your quiz on time in the weeks of assessment. You must attend your allocated tutorial.</li>\n<li>If you arrive late to the session, you will not receive additional time to complete the quiz.</li>\n<li>The quizzes allow one (1) typed double sided A4 Page Cheat Sheet with standard margins, 1.5 line spacing minimum, and 12pt Font Size (Times New Roman or Calibri Fonts Required). All notes MUST be in English. Cheat Sheets must be handed in with your quiz at time for submission. This will be checked and non-compliance with these requirements accounts for academic misconduct.</li>\n<li>Only UQ approved calculators are allowed.</li>\n<li>More details regarding the format of the quiz will be posted to Blackboard under Assessment.</li>\n</ul>\n<button class=\"collapsible__toggle\">\n<span class=\"collapsible__open link--icon icon--standard--arrow-down-1\">Read full task description</span>\n<span class=\"collapsible__close link--icon icon--standard--arrow-up-1\">Hide full task description</span>\n</button>\n</div>",
            "submission_guidelines": "<p>Submitted in tutorial.</p>",
            "deferral_or_extension": "<p>You may be able to <a href=\"https://my.uq.edu.au/information-and-services/manage-my-program/exams-and-assessment/applying-assessment-extension\">apply for an extension</a>.</p>",
            "late_submission": "<p>You will receive a mark of 0 if this assessment is <a href=\"https://policies.uq.edu.au/document/view-current.php?id=184\">submitted late</a>.</p>",
